1. *Kakav* si ti čovek? (What kind of man are you?)

2. *Kakva* je njegova budućnost? (What is his future?)

3. Da li je *kakva* razlika? (Is there any difference?)

4. *Kakvo* je tvoje mišljenje? (What is your opinion?)

5. Ona se pita *kakvi* su njegovi planovi. (She wonders what his plans are.)

6. Svi se pitaju *kakvo* će biti vreme. (Everyone is wondering what the weather will be like.)

7. *Kakvo* je stanje u zemlji? (What is the state of the country?)